---
// CSS-only animated terminal: cycles through three gitbasher flows.
// Each "scene" fades into view in sequence so the file stays tiny.
---
<div class="terminal demo" role="img" aria-label="Animated terminal demo: gitb commit ai, gitb branch newd, gitb wip up">
  <div class="terminal-header">
    <span class="dot red"></span>
    <span class="dot yellow"></span>
    <span class="dot green"></span>
    <span class="title">~/projects/my-app — gitb</span>
  </div>
  <div class="terminal-body">
    <pre aria-hidden="true"><div class="scene scene-1">
<span class="prompt-arrow">❯</span> <span class="cmd">gitb commit ai</span>

<span class="info">Step 1.</span> Analyzing staged changes…
<span class="dim">  M src/auth/session.ts</span>
<span class="dim">  A src/auth/refresh.ts</span>

<span class="info">Step 2.</span> Asking <span class="tip">ollama</span> (<span class="tip">qwen3:8b</span>) to write a conventional commit…
  <span class="ok">✓</span> Generated message in 1.2s

<span class="info">Step 3.</span> Confirm:
  <span class="tip">feat(auth):</span> add silent token refresh on expiry

<span class="ok">✓</span> Committed <span class="dim">a3f1c8e</span>
<span class="tip">💡</span> Tip: <span class="cmd">gitb push</span> to publish
</div><div class="scene scene-2">
<span class="prompt-arrow">❯</span> <span class="cmd">gitb branch newd</span>

<span class="info">Step 1.</span> Fetching <span class="tip">origin/main</span>…
<span class="info">Step 2.</span> Fast-forwarding <span class="tip">main</span>…  <span class="ok">✓</span>
<span class="info">Step 3.</span> Branch name:
  <span class="warn">feat/</span><span class="cmd">payment-refunds</span>

<span class="ok">✓</span> Switched to <span class="tip">feat/payment-refunds</span> from updated <span class="tip">main</span>
</div><div class="scene scene-3">
<span class="prompt-arrow">❯</span> <span class="cmd">gitb wip up</span>

<span class="info">Step 1.</span> Stashing 4 changed files…  <span class="ok">✓</span>
<span class="info">Step 2.</span> Pushing backup → <span class="tip">origin/wip/feat-payment-refunds</span>  <span class="ok">✓</span>
<span class="info">Step 3.</span> Working tree clean

<span class="ok">✓</span> WIP saved. Restore anywhere with <span class="cmd">gitb wip down</span>
<span class="tip">💡</span> Your code never left your laptop except as a backup branch.
</div></pre>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .demo {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .demo .terminal-body {
    position: relative;
    height: 290px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .demo pre {
    margin: 0;
    background: transparent;
    border: 0;
    padding: 0;
    position: relative;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .scene {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: cycle 18s infinite;
    white-space: pre-wrap;
  }

  .scene-1 {
    animation-delay: 0s;
  }
  .scene-2 {
    animation-delay: 6s;
  }
  .scene-3 {
    animation-delay: 12s;
  }

  @keyframes cycle {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(8px);
    }
    3% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    30% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    33% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 0;
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .scene {
      animation: none;
    }
    .scene-1 {
      opacity: 1;
    }
    .scene-2,
    .scene-3 {
      opacity: 0;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .demo .terminal-body {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      height: 320px;
    }
  }
</style>
